# Auth Service (zv-auth-service) - Project Context

## Service Location

- **Local Path**: `/home/yousef/Documents/workspace/zonevast/services/zv-auth-service/`
- **Framework**: Django + Django REST Framework
- **Database**: PostgreSQL (`dev0`), shared DB with other services
- **Port**: `8010` (local development)

## Deployment

| Environment | URL / Lambda Name |
|---|---|
| **Test (dev)** | `https://test.zonevast.com/api/v1/auth/auth/` |
| **Prod** | `https://api.zonevast.com/api/v1/auth/auth/` |
| **Lambda dev** | `zonevast-auth-service-dev` |
| **Local** | `http://localhost:8010/api/v1/auth/auth/` |

### Deploy Commands

```bash
cd /home/yousef/Documents/workspace/zonevast/services/zv-auth-service/

# Deploy to dev (test.zonevast.com)
zappa deploy dev       # First time
zappa update dev       # Subsequent updates

# Deploy to prod
zappa update prod

# View logs
zappa tail dev
zappa tail prod
```

