## How to Access Online

### Test Environment (Swagger UI)
- **Swagger**: `https://test.zonevast.com/api/v1/auth/auth/` (root shows endpoints)
- **Direct API**: Use `https://test.zonevast.com/api/v1/auth/auth/token/` for login

### Required Headers
```
Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
X-Project-ID: 11
Content-Type: application/json
```

## API Endpoints

All endpoints under `/api/v1/auth/auth/`:

### Authentication
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|---|
| POST | `token/` | JWT login (returns access + refresh) |
| POST | `token/refresh/` | Refresh access token |
| POST | `token/change_project/` | Switch project context |
| POST | `login/` | Legacy token+session login |
| POST | `logout/` | Logout |

### Registration & Verification
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|---|
| POST | `register/` | Register new user (sends OTP) |
| POST | `send-otp/` | Resend OTP to email |
| POST | `verify-otp/` | Verify OTP to activate account |
| POST | `password/reset/` | Reset password with OTP |
| POST | `password/change/` | Change password (needs current) |

### User Management
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|---|
| GET/PATCH | `user/` | Get/update current user details |
| POST | `user/upload-image/` | Upload profile image |
| POST | `user/language/` | Update language (en/ar) |

### User Profile & Data
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|---|
| CRUD | `profile/` | User profile (bio, gender, birth_date, etc.) |
| CRUD | `payment-card/` | Payment cards |
| CRUD | `address/` | User addresses |
| GET | `country/` | List countries |
| GET | `region/<slug>/` | Regions by country |

### Dev Only
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|---|
| POST | `test-users/` | Create test users (dev/test only) |

## Models

### User (AbstractUser)
- `language` (en/ar), `phone`, `orders_count`, `wins_count`
- Standard Django user fields: username, email, first_name, etc.

### UserProfile
- `profile_picture`, `bio`, `phone`, `birth_date`, `gender`
- `company_name`, `position_title`

### Address
- `address_type` (home/work/other), `street_address`, `city`, `governorate`
- `postal_code`, `country`, `nearest_landmark`

### PaymentCard
- `provider`, `card_number`, `cardholder_name`, `cvv`, `expire_date`

## Auth Flow for Mobile App (Forsa)

1. **Register**: `POST register/` → creates inactive user + sends OTP
2. **Verify OTP**: `POST verify-otp/` → activates user (dev mode: bypassed)
3. **Login**: `POST token/` → returns `access` + `refresh` JWT tokens
4. **Use Token**: Add `Authorization: Bearer <access>` to all requests
5. **Refresh**: `POST token/refresh/` when access token expires

